<p>Many people do not realize how much animal-cruelty touches our everyday lives. Aside from the foods we consume, practices in fashion and beauty are strong culprits of a cruel animal industry. At MERSI, we believe that all beings are important, and deserve to be valued. That is why we are dedicated to making alternatives that are high-quality and accessible to everyone.</p>
