<p>What is the difference between animal leather and vegan leather? To begin with, vegan leather contains zero animal ingredients or remnants. It is more ethical and sustainable than traditional animal leather, due to its manufacturing process and overall need for less resources such as water and land to be utilized in its creation.</p>
</div>
<div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm--lg gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs" data-exc=""></div>
